<body>
<p>Sir / Madam,&nbsp;
    <br />
    <br />As you are aware, Canaccede International Management Ltd is processing Bank of Nova Scotia insolvent accounts.&nbsp;
    <br />
    <br />We have received your package and Bank of Nova Scotia has requested some additional information on the account listed.&nbsp;
    <br />
    <br />Please be advised that BNS is not able to locate the debtor, please provide us with the account #, VIN and/or SIN #.&nbsp;
    <br />
    <br />If any errors occurred in the transmission of the attachment, please contact Canaccede at;&nbsp;
